                         Content: v.--> <inline font-size="9pt" font-style="italic"> [Note: <inline font-style="italic">V.c.</inline>4.<inline font-style="italic">n.</inline>17.] </inline> and at the last they turne whitish againe, <!--An internal link should have been created here,
