                         constitute the link.
                         Target: 
                         Content: Cap.7.n.63.--></block><block line-height="1" text-indent="1em" space-before.optimum="0pt" space-before.maximum="12pt"><inline font-size="9pt" font-style="italic"> [Note: 62. <inline font-style="italic">The Bees excellencies.</inline>] </inline> The Bee therefore excelling in many qualities, it is fitly said in the Proverbe, <block/> <inline font-style="italic">As <list-block provisional-distance-between-starts="18pt" provisional-label-separation="6pt" text-indent="0em" margin-right="10pt" space-before="6pt" space-after="6pt"><list-item space-before.optimum="4pt"><list-item-label end-indent="label-end()">
