                         Content: V.n.1.&2.-->] </inline> that grosse and earthy stuffe is no whit comparable to this Celestiall <inline font-style="italic" font-weight="normal">Nectar.</inline> Although some queint &amp; Ladilike palats (whom nothing but that which is farre saught and deare bought can please) unhappily neglect it. In preserving Fruits it hath more power through the viscositie thereof. Also Conserves and Syrups being made with Honie<!--An internal link should have been created here,
